  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/436272ae3a7558f89e47b9d612947d08.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/d85fe0ab1caadae4456f38c53a24699c.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Northend Tower Defense is a unique tower defense game that unlocks and deploys powerful troops and vehicles, upgrades your army, and holds the line in an intense, multi-battlefield setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/d6859f23a957f511486e30d23e49c292.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/d6859f23a957f511486e30d23e49c292.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the chaos of battle, where every decision can mean the difference between victory and defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/397e8498e4c92b2f96545917cd7d2a87.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/397e8498e4c92b2f96545917cd7d2a87.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the intensity of multi-front warfare, and feel the adrenaline rush as you face relentless enemy waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/ab15877bbd6364cb507fadda4f829578.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/ab15877bbd6364cb507fadda4f829578.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/f8c0349d846028932031e2361da5e20b.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NETD deploys you in big battles of +20 different units, +77 unique upgrades, 4 passive powers, and 5 special abilities. Command a diverse array of units, upgrade and customize your units to adapt to the ever-changing battlefield conditions, and secure your victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/bdfa74430680ca93feb6a25d6862e2ab.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/bdfa74430680ca93feb6a25d6862e2ab.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/425ca13ad2f1dcc39343f181314d2eac.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/425ca13ad2f1dcc39343f181314d2eac.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/ecc9c79ccd77c8dd4b806b2feffadb0f.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From beach landings to desert trenches, Northend Tower Defense's rich level design allows players to continually gain unique gameplay experiences each round. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/64dfed4b720ce7f6097caa0ef5960fc5.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/64dfed4b720ce7f6097caa0ef5960fc5.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/8963c2415ff1b0d25f8c9645f70fbd37.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NETD Zombies introduces an entirely new gameplay experience. Deploy a variety of newly designed traps and pick up powerful airdrops, and face off against massive zombie hordes with your army. There are over 12 new powerful upgrades at your disposal. Each upgrade features 4 different levels, allowing you to shock, burn, electrify, and blow up your enemies in increasingly devastating ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/27d4b8d6a5e64599435e6b868b1be090.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/27d4b8d6a5e64599435e6b868b1be090.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/a1cf10424b1e595965b1042d10951aa0.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/a1cf10424b1e595965b1042d10951aa0.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/436272ae3a7558f89e47b9d612947d08.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/d85fe0ab1caadae4456f38c53a24699c.avif?t=1773721040\" width=630 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Northend Tower Defense is a unique tower defense game that unlocks and deploys powerful troops and vehicles, upgrades your army, and holds the line in an intense, multi-battlefield setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/d6859f23a957f511486e30d23e49c292.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/d6859f23a957f511486e30d23e49c292.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the chaos of battle, where every decision can mean the difference between victory and defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/397e8498e4c92b2f96545917cd7d2a87.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/397e8498e4c92b2f96545917cd7d2a87.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experi