l. Each upgrade features 4 different levels, allowing you to shock, burn, electrify, and blow up your enemies in increasingly devastating ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/27d4b8d6a5e64599435e6b868b1be090.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/27d4b8d6a5e64599435e6b868b1be090.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/a1cf10424b1e595965b1042d10951aa0.poster.avif?t=1773721040\" width=620 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669170/extras/a1cf10424b1e595965b1042d10951aa0.webm?t=1773721040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
